sankranti is a telugu film , produced by r. b. choudary under super good films , and directed by muppalaneni shiva .   it stars venkatesh , arti agarwal , srikanth , sneha , and sangeetha in lead roles .   the music was composed by s.a. rajkumar .   " sankranti " is festival celebrated in india .   it is a remake of the 2001 tamil blockbuster aanandham , directed by n. linguswamy with mammootty and devayani in the lead roles .